column2: SELECT search_id AS up_id, ra AS up_ra, dec AS up_dec  FROM MyDB.AKARI_lost_pos  CREATE TABLE #tmp ( 	up_id int, 	objid bigint ) INSERT INTO #tmp EXEC spGetNeighbors #    SELECT DISTINCT  	po.objid AS phot_id, po.ra AS phot_ra, po.dec AS phot_dec, po.l AS phot_glon, po.b AS phot_glat,  	po.clean AS phot_clean,  	(po.calibStatus_i & #) AS calibStatus_i,  	po.modelmag_i AS modmag_i, po.modelmagerr_i AS moderr_i, po.extinction_i AS extinct_i,  	wa.w1cc_map AS wise_w1cc_map, wa.w2cc_map AS wise_w2cc_map, wa.w3cc_map AS wise_w3cc_map, wa.w4cc_map AS wise_w4cc_map,  	wa.w3m AS wise_w3m,  	wa.w3snr AS wise_w3snr INTO mydb.tmp2     FROM #tmp tmp 	     INNER JOIN DR1#.PhotoPrimary po ON po.objid      = tmp.objid 	     INNER JOIN DR1#.WISE_xmatch  wx ON wx.sdss_objid = po.objid 	     INNER JOIN DR1#.WISE_allsky  wa ON wa.cntr       = wx.wise_cntr
